msgid "%(org_name)s has new boundaries"
msgstr "Mae gan %(org_name)s ffiniau newydd"

#: wcivf/apps/elections/templates/elections/boundary_reviews_view.html:54
msgid ""
"A new set of constituency and regional boundaries will be used for the 2026 "
"Scottish parliament elections. The boundaries of all constituencies and "
"regions have been reviewed by the independent organisation"
msgstr ""
"Bydd set newydd o ffiniau etholaethau yn cael eu defnyddio ar gyfer etholiad "
"2024. Mae hyn yn golygu y gallai eich etholaeth fod wedi newid ers yr "
"etholiad diwethaf."

#: wcivf/apps/elections/templates/elections/boundary_reviews_view.html:60
msgid "to take account of population changes since 2011."
msgstr "i ystyried newidiadau yn y boblogaeth ers 2011."

#: wcivf/apps/elections/templates/elections/boundary_reviews_view.html:63
msgid ""
"This means that your constituency or region may have changed shape or name "
"since the last election, or you may be in a new constituency or region."
msgstr ""
"Bydd set newydd o ffiniau etholaethau yn cael eu defnyddio ar gyfer yr "
"etholiad nesaf. Mae hyn yn golygu y gallai eich etholaeth fod wedi newid."

#: wcivf/apps/elections/templates/elections/boundary_reviews_view.html:67
msgid ""
"The way you vote has changed. When voting for your Members of the Senedd, "
"you will now vote on one ballot paper, instead of two as previously. You "
"will vote once for a single party or independent candidate, and seats will "
"be allocated using proportional representation. Party candidates will be "
"elected in the order they appear on their party list."
msgstr ""
"2.\tMae sut rydych chi’n pleidleisio wedi newid. Yn awr, pan fyddwch chi’n "
"pleidleisio dros ymgeisydd i fod yn Aelod o’r Senedd, byddwch yn defnyddio "
"un papur pleidleisio yn hytrach na dau. Byddwch yn bwrw un bleidlais i un "
"blaid neu ymgeisydd annibynnol, a bydd y seddau’n cael eu dyrannu gan "
"ddefnyddio cynrychiolaeth gyfrannol. Bydd ymgeiswyr y pleidiau’n cael eu "
"hethol yn y drefn y maen nhw’n ymddangos ar restr eu plaid."

#: wcivf/apps/elections/templates/elections/boundary_reviews_view.html:74
msgid ""
"These changes mean that you will have a new constituency. Each constituency "
"will elect six members, and the overall number of Senedd members is "
"increasing from 60 to 96. Senedd elections will happen every four years."
msgstr ""
"Mae’r newidiadau hyn yn golygu y bydd gennych chi etholaeth newydd. Bydd pob "
"etholaeth yn ethol chwe aelod, ac mae nifer o aelodau’r Senedd yn cynyddu o "
"60 i 96. Bydd etholiadau’r Senedd yn digwydd bob pedair blynedd."

#: wcivf/apps/elections/templates/elections/boundary_reviews_view.html:83
msgid "Learn more about the Senedd changes"
msgstr "Dysgwch fwy am y newidiadau i’r Senedd."

#: wcivf/apps/elections/templates/elections/boundary_reviews_view.html:91
#, python-format
msgid "Your %(division_unit_cap)s has not changed"
msgstr "Nid yw eich %(division_unit_cap)s wedi newid"

#: wcivf/apps/elections/templates/elections/boundary_reviews_view.html:96
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Your %(division_unit)s has not been significantly affected by the boundary "
"review. Whilst there may have been minor adjustments to the boundary, no "
"houses have been added or removed, and its name, <strong>%(old_name)s</"
"strong>, is unchanged from the last election."
msgstr ""
"9.\tNi chafodd yr adolygiad ffiniau effaith sylweddol ar eich "
"%(division_unit)s. Efallai bod y ffiniau wedi cael eu haddasu ychydig, ond "
"nid oes unrhyw dai wedi'u hychwanegu na’u tynnu, ac nid yw ei enw, "
"<strong>%(old_name)s</strong>, wedi newid ers yr etholiad diwethaf."

