msgstr ""
"Yn yr etholiad seneddol diwethaf, <strong>%(old_name)s</strong> oedd eich "
"%(division_unit)s chi. Mae ganddo enw newydd bellach, sef "
"<strong>%(new_name)s</strong>. Nid yw ffiniau'r %(division_unit)s wedi newid "
"yn sylweddol."

#: wcivf/apps/elections/templates/elections/boundary_reviews_view.html:152
#, python-format
