"mwyach."

#: wcivf/apps/parties/templates/parties/parties_view.html:26
msgid ""
"A party can become deregistered through choice, or because it failed to "
"renew its annual registration status."
msgstr ""
"Gall plaid gael ei datgofrestru trwy ddewis, neu oherwydd iddi fethu ag "
"adnewyddu ei statws cofrestru blynyddol."

